Step 1: Identify all nouns (actors in problem statement)
	> Student, graduate students, post graduate students, 
	hostelite, day scholar, faculty member, admin staff,
	lecturer, visiting members, head of department
Step 2: Identify all activities (use cases, connect actors to use cases)
	> course, semester, marked projects/assignments, attendance
Step 3: Identify the relationship (generalization, specialization, includes)
	> Semester includes a course, course includes assignments,
	course includes projects, course includes attendance,
	course includes lecturer, course includes students
	> Generalization - Specialization
		student - graduate student or post graduate student
		student - hostelite or dayscholar
		lecturer - full time or visiting member